# Local development environment for basket-estadistics
# This file is gitignored. Never commit it.

# The app uses Neon Postgres. DATABASE_URL lives in .env — do NOT override it
# here: .env.local takes precedence and a stale value silently breaks the app.
# (The old SQLite file:./data/basket.db setup is gone.)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# YouTube Data API v3 — https://console.cloud.google.com
# Needed only for the highlights feature on player profiles.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
